# Admin Settings

You can configure admin settings in `asset:/config/admin.php`.

## `OP::_ADMIN_IP_`

When you access from the IP address set here, developer mode will be enabled.
The `OP()->isAdmin()` will return `true` based on the IP address set here.
This value affects `D()` and `OP()->Error()`.
Please set the value of `OP::_ADMIN_IP_` to the administratorâ€™s IP address.

```php
[
    OP::_ADMIN_IP_ => '192.168.100.100'
]
```

## `OP::_ADMIN_MAIL_`

Error messages will be sent to this email address.

```php
[
    OP::_ADMIN_MAIL_ => 'info@onepiece-framework.com'
]
```

## `OP::_ADMIN_FROM_`

This email address will be used as the "from" of the admin email.

```php
[
    OP::_ADMIN_FROM_ => 'noreply@onepiece-framework.com'
]
```
